item.title: Wtf...?
item.dc:creator: @ExtremeX-Scape Ryley
item.description:
@ExtremeX-Scape wrote:

Okay, there is NO server editing when trying to change the servers IP, that’s all related to the client,
second, go into the GUI class and change the IP in there to ‘127.0.0.1’ same for the client class,

In the GUI, the IP in there needs to be ‘online’ or port forwarded for the GUI to recognize it, which it needs to be in order to run the client.
